Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.64,0:01:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走嘛  走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.50,0:01:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.18,0:01:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之跟我们走就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.49,0:01:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走嘛  走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走嘛  走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.23,0:01:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你很久了  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.83,0:02:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.98,0:02:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长的命令拒绝不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  进去吧  进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.31,0:02:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有时会发出很可疑的骚动  还会听到奇怪的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有感觉到什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.19,0:02:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…  我也不会感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管夏目你怎么否认  我始终相信你有种特别的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许你并不喜欢  但我觉得那是很了不起的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该更自信一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  说来西村和北本呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.01,0:02:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用去管那些不相信的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实像是会有妖怪的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多轨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.81,0:03:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有意思  我也一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  {\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}笹{\r}田同学  我们去对面看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目就去看那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.89,0:03:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啦  行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:25.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想跟夏目…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫多轨的小姑娘  还挺机灵的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  我们赶快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个地方确实不宜久留
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为什么  真的有什么在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  在对方没发现我们之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.11,0:03:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  喂  你去哪！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话多轨她们也有危险  我去叫她们回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:01.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的声音  小孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:09.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  说不定那不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棺材？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  打开！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:49.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在里面？等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就打开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:13.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美的上勾拳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子怎么会被关在这里面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从气味来看  似乎不是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在玩捉迷藏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是不小心盖子掉下来  就出不来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像听到有声音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:37.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  没什么  你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾  什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在这里  猫咪！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧…兴趣真差
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石尾海？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三班那个  就是被怪人追的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还说可能是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是因为父母回家都很晚  他才变得说这种话了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他被人欺负吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会  不知怎么的他朋友很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.53,0:06:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BYEBYE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.75,0:06:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫咪老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:42.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你把我关进箱子里的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说不是我了  我是来给你送东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.23,0:06:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:53.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这家伙在追着你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚开！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.34,0:07:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看  他还带着只超丑的猫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.09,0:07:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好土！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丑？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是猪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚远点！豆芽！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜板！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朴树！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人妖！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚开！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先逃吧  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  逃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准再来！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:24.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是  轻轻松松
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  海你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉唉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说不定不会应付小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:42.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（豆芽）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:43.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（菜板）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:44.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（朴树）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:45.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（人妖）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比跟妖怪对峙受到的伤害还大…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真够烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好  这个忘记给他了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.88,0:07:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  名牌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:08:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  老师  你帮我带给那孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你200日元
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！居然想用区区200日元就打发我这高贵的妖怪！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要纸的！纸钞！给我福泽谕吉！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:11.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（福泽谕吉：万元钞）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被妖怪追着…那孩子也能看见妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  田沼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看见妖怪的孩子…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:35.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  也不像被人欺负
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.77,0:08:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.38,0:08:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了他  那个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是破坏了约定  就吃了他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.51,0:08:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:11.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它说的小鬼是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  多轨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:23.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  刚才…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  你是第一次见到田沼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是五班的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:34.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话等一下再说  赶快离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家里有书上写了  说这附近会吸引妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸引妖怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你流血了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候…  是刚才那家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.64,0:09:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血的味道会引来妖怪  快走吧  你也是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖辈是阴阳师？所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  这就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.22,0:10:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是很凶暴的妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不能对妖怪心软
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它们与人不同  是邪恶的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫海的孩子  真的能看到妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚  不过如果能看到的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:34.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想保护他？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到不能坐视不管  就会马上出手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事  或许是我太傲慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果  只觉得是自己在找麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久之前  还全都怪在妖怪头上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:34.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妖怪吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:45.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（你掉的东西）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉…掉的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好  猫咪老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  会给你的  回去给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:01.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忍不住了～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.48,0:12:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又  又是你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.98,0:12:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫咪  猫咪～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的兴趣真差劲啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟在我后面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.48,0:12:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不是你吗  不是你在追我  把我关进箱子里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.23,0:12:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…之前的  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…说你是豆芽  菜板  人妖什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  啊  不…没关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好笑的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见  我道过歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.44,0:12:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于那个追着你的家伙  告诉警察比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:12:59.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  跟他们说了也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会没用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我道过歉了  你就别管我了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别耍这种无聊的脾气！等到事情严重了就太晚了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.66,0:13:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起  我这么大声
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.86,0:13:33.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没断  过几天就不会痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小孩子弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底该如何把我的担心传达给他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对妖怪反而交往得更轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:28.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没想给你添麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是刚好看到了  你的手受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想会不会是为了救我  被追着我的家伙攻击了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这次就由我来保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才跟过来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.19,0:15:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里人还没回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一个人吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人说要保护我  这还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我等一下  你把我当成什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:23.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师是我的保镖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准忘！也不好笑！真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  小妖怪而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追着我来了的话  它的目标就不是海吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它盯上海了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  但是它说过要吃掉小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃小孩子的妖怪有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:15:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你想太多了  区区小妖怪的戏言而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:01.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说小妖怪  我刚才还被它弄伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？在我不知道的时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一点小伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子！虽然你被吃掉我就能得到友人帐是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.91,0:16:15.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但让那种小妖怪弄伤我的东西  我心情是很微妙的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常微妙！你懂不懂夏目！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这微妙的心情！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.15,0:16:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微妙——
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:30.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那如果海看不到妖怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯上海的不是妖怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁把海关进棺材里的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  你在看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真可爱  是在等人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.33,0:16:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.90,0:17:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想  保护那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:13.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以来  我每天放学后都和海一起度过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多轨教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.69,0:17:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下就一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.54,0:17:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.48,0:17:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告诉我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个箱子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你不愿意就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.87,0:17:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早些时候  我就觉得被谁盯着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来发现电线杆后面有人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:18:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始以为只是变态  就没太在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  这应该在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天  我被那家伙追赶  跑进了那栋房子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是想躲进那个箱子里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果就出不来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子被锁上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锁上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候  我记得没有锁…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.32,0:18:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多轨看不见  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.99,0:18:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  这么说  夏目也看得见那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.22,0:18:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多轨  这里有妖怪！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带着海往这边逃  你别追过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:18:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:18:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.22,0:19:12.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.32,0:19:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:15.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.31,0:19:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…  糟糕  被引过来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.01,0:19:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海  快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.09,0:19:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫咪老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我  放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.83,0:19:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我放它走的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:20:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉的话你会很烦  而且我是个美食家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.71,0:20:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它的妖气吸走了不少  应该不会再来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道是这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.03,0:20:11.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多轨面无血色地跑来找我  过来一看就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要到什么时候才会长记性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多轨…是吗  老师  谢谢你  得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别摸鼻子！很痒的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  好厉害啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目能驯服妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.61,0:20:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是驯服  是它救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目！海！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多轨！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.06,0:20:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  你们没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  多亏了老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.17,0:20:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫咪！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.42,0:20:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了够了够了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.54,0:20:51.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.01,0:20:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海能看见妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.09,0:20:58.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么追赶他的是刚才那个妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.89,0:21:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得好像还没结束…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他把海关进棺材里的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.99,0:21:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名  名取先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.19,0:21:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  这次特意不想把你卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:36.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你自己牵扯过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  把海关进棺材里的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是关进去  而是封印
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.23,0:21:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是不要接近那孩子比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:52.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  到底是怎么回事  名取先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.07,0:21:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.60,0:22:01.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.02,0:23:50.02,biaoti1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,550)}人与妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海竟然是妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.55,0:23:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了消灭他才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.97,0:23:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他干了什么！海做了什么要被人消灭的事吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.27,0:23:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  你也该下定决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.88,0:23:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说重要的  到底是人  还是妖怪


